/* As an example,
   Take Out Orders: [1, 3, 5]
    Dine In Orders: [2, 4, 6]
     Served Orders: [1, 2, 4, 6, 5, 3]
would not be first-come, first-served, since order 3 was requested before order 5 but order 5 was served first.

But,
